And I decided to port a couple of FF7 songs to the Sega Mega Drive using Deflemask. The Mega Drive's chip is definitely weird and interesting, some things are ridiculously easy to do and others almost impossible. I like to cheat and use a single 4-op instrument to simulate 2 2-op instruments, in order to get more channels.<br />What do you guys think ?<br /><br />EDIT : Changed the song according to comments (see below).<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38">Bregalad</a> — Sun Mar 05, 2017 2:49 pm</p><hr />
